description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Totally non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, all broadcast live to members. Today's update is RD 3 of 4. This was November's live match now edited for your enjoyment!
If you thought the first parts of the match were hard fought and brutal then you're in for the RD3 of your lifetime. All 4 girls leave it all on the mat. The action is brutal, rough, and intense. One team sucks it up and pulls out a hard fought victory, the crowd goes absolutely bat shit crazy for what transpire at the end of the match.
Two girls go down in defeat, two girls celebrate the victory of champions. An amazing finish to brutal non-scripted fight you will ever see.
title: 3pts separate these 4 girls in the final wrestling RD Who is going to open the can of whip ass?
